column5: I went 1 for 3 today, 75 back 50 down roughly on the riggers.I had my line release once, with nothing to show for I began marking fish at ???? fow and I had a quick hit in which I landed  After about another hr or so of trolling my line went off again and gone just as fast When I arrived home,  I told my oldest that I needed to take a pic of her and the fish Finally after all these years, she was slimed as well
